                  "requirementText": "a. Develop, document, and maintain under configuration control, a current baseline configuration of the system; and\rb. Review and update the baseline configuration of the system:\r     1. [Assignment: organization-defined frequency];\r     2. When required due to [Assignment: organization-defined circumstances]; and\r     3. When system components are installed or upgraded.",
