                  "category": null,
                  "subcategory": null,
                  "questionGroupHeadingID": 0,
                  "title": "IA-4 (4)",
                  "requirementText": "Manage individual identifiers by uniquely identifying each individual as [Assignment: organization-defined characteristic identifying individual status].",
                  "salLevels": [
                    "H",
                    "M"
                  ],
                  "supplementalInfo": "Characteristics that identify the status of individuals include contractors, foreign nationals, and non-organizational users. Identifying the status of individuals by these characteristics provides additional information about the people with whom organizational personnel are communicating. For example, it might be useful for a government employee to know that one of the individuals on an email message is a contractor.",
