                  "setName": null,
                  "category": null,
                  "subcategory": null,
                  "questionGroupHeadingID": 0,
                  "title": "MP-3",
                  "requirementText": "a. Mark system media indicating the distribution limitations, handling caveats, and applicable security markings (if any) of the information; and\rb. Exempt [Assignment: organization-defined types of system media] from marking if the media remain within [Assignment: organization-defined controlled areas].",
