                  "subcategory": null,
                  "questionGroupHeadingID": 0,
                  "title": "MP-4",
                  "requirementText": "a. Physically control and securely store [Assignment: organization-defined types of digital and/or non-digital media] within [Assignment: organization-defined controlled areas]; and\rb. Protect system media types defined in MP-4a until the media are destroyed or sanitized using approved equipment, techniques, and procedures.",
