                  "requirementText": "a. Implement a process for ensuring that organizational plans for conducting security and privacy testing, training, and monitoring activities associated with organizational systems:\r     1. Are developed and maintained; and\r     2. Continue to be executed; and\rb. Review testing, training, and monitoring plans for consistency with the organizational risk management strategy and organization-wide priorities for risk response actions.",
