                  "requirementText": "a. Develop and maintain an accurate accounting of disclosures of personally identifiable information, including:\r     1. Date, nature, and purpose of each disclosure; and\r     2. Name and address, or other contact information of the individual or organization to which the disclosure was made;\rb. Retain the accounting of disclosures for the length of the time the personally identifiable information is maintained or five years after the disclosure is made, whichever is longer; and\rc. Make the accounting of disclosures available to the individual to whom the personally identifiable information relates upon request.",
