                  "requirementText": "a. Identify and document:\r     1. Assumptions affecting risk assessments, risk responses, and risk monitoring;\r     2. Constraints affecting risk assessments, risk responses, and risk monitoring;\r     3. Priorities and trade-offs considered by the organization for managing risk; and\r     4. Organizational risk tolerance;\rb. Distribute the results of risk framing activities to [Assignment: organization-defined personnel]; and\rc. Review and update risk framing considerations [Assignment: organization-defined frequency].",
