                  "questionGroupHeadingID": 0,
                  "title": "PS-1",
                  "requirementText": "a. Develop, document, and disseminate to [Assignment: organization-defined personnel or roles]:\r     1. [Selection (one or more): Organization-level; Mission/business process-level; System-level] personnel security policy that:\r          (a) Addresses purpose, scope, roles, responsibilities, management commitment, coordination among organizational entities, and \r          compliance; and\r          (b) Is consistent with applicable laws, executive orders, directives, regulations, policies, standards, and guidelines; and\r      2. Procedures to facilitate the implementation of the personnel security policy and the associated personnel security controls;\rb. Designate an [Assignment: organization-defined official] to manage the development, documentation, and dissemination of the personnel security policy and procedures; and\rc. Review and update the current personnel security:\r     1. Policy [Assignment: organization-defined frequency] and following [Assignment: organization-defined events]; and\r     2. Procedures [Assignment: organization-defined frequency] and following [Assignment: organization-defined events].",
