                  "requirementText": "Upon termination of individual employment:\ra. Disable system access within [Assignment: organization-defined time period];\rb. Terminate or revoke any authenticators and credentials associated with the individual;\rc. Conduct exit interviews that include a discussion of [Assignment: organization-defined information security topics];\rd. Retrieve all security-related organizational system-related property; and\re. Retain access to organizational information and systems formerly controlled by terminated individual.",
