                  "requirementText": "Require the developer of the system, system component, or system service to:\r(a) Define quality metrics at the beginning of the development process; and\r(b) Provide evidence of meeting the quality metrics [Selection (one or more): [Assignment: organization-defined frequency]; [Assignment: organization-defined program review milestones]; upon delivery].",
