                  "requirementText": "Require the developer of the system, system component, or system service to perform a criticality analysis:\r(a) At the following decision points in the system development life cycle: [Assignment: organization-defined decision points in the system development life cycle]; and\r(b) At the following level of rigor: [Assignment: organization-defined breadth and depth of criticality analysis].",
