                  "supplementalInfo": "Managing the processing of personally identifiable information is an important aspect of protecting an individual&#8217;s privacy. Applying, monitoring for, and documenting exceptions to processing rules ensure that personally identifiable information is processed only in accordance with established privacy requirements.",
