                  "requirementText": "(a) Employ the following tools and techniques to analyze the characteristics and behavior of malicious code: [Assignment: organization-defined tools and techniques]; and\r(b) Incorporate the results from malicious code analysis into organizational incident response and flaw remediation processes.",
